3. Data Preparation (Power Query)
Import & Model

Imported CSV into Power BI.

Verified headers and data types:

Year â†’ Whole Number

Sales â†’ Decimal Number

Artist/Genre â†’ Text

Cleaning Steps

Removed blank rows/columns.

